{
  "texts": [
    "We later separate a portion of this dataset, e.g., 1500 depressive tweets for human annotation which we call DSD-Clinician-Tweets dataset.",
    "Details of the annotation process are described in Sect. 3.4.",
    "We train our first DSD model using this dataset, then use this model to harvest more samples from DTR.",
    "An outline of the DTR and DSD-Clinician-Tweets curation process is provided in Fig. 3.",
    "We describe the details of this process in Sect. 4.2, but describe each of its building blocks in the next sections."
  ]
}